<varlistentry id="options.CustomCursor">
	<term>CustomCursor <emphasis remap='I'>path</emphasis></term>
	<listitem>
		<para>Adds a custom cursor from the search paths. AfterStep searches the following paths in addition to the system Xorg/Xfree paths: ~/.afterstep/desktop/cursors/ and $SHAREDIR/afterstep/desktop/cursors/.</para>
		<para>Note: under Xorg, this is probably depreciated. Current Xorg uses the Xcursor library to load cursor data from a single file.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
